---
---

<section id="workflow" class="py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight text-ink md:text-4xl text-balance">
        The fastest programming workflow on the market.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-ink-muted">
        Legacy platforms give you endless menus and clunky drag-and-drop builders. WAGMI lets you type naturally and handles the formatting instantly.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="relative rounded-xl border border-warm-border bg-card p-8 shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="mb-6 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-cobalt-soft text-cobalt">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:pen-linear" stroke-width="1.5" class="text-2xl"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium tracking-tight text-ink">1. Type how you think</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Use messy shorthand, abbreviations, and quick notes. Just get the workout out of your head and onto the screen as fast as you can type.
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-md bg-parchment-alt p-3 border border-warm-border font-mono">
          <p class="text-xs font-medium text-ink-muted">Mike prep w1 d1. squat 4x8 @70%, bench 3x10, acc: db rows 3x12</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="relative rounded-xl border border-warm-border bg-card p-8 shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="mb-6 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-cobalt-soft text-dusty">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:layers-minimalistic-linear" stroke-width="1.5" class="text-2xl"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium tracking-tight text-ink">2. We structure it</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Our underlying system parses your shorthand into clean, structured programs perfectly formatted with periods, rep schemes, and exercises.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <iconify-icon icon="solar:check-circle-linear" class="text-emerald-500"></iconify-icon>
            <span class="text-xs text-ink-muted">Matched exercise database</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <iconify-icon icon="solar:check-circle-linear" class="text-emerald-500"></iconify-icon>
            <span class="text-xs text-ink-muted">Calculated percentages</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <iconify-icon icon="solar:check-circle-linear" class="text-emerald-500"></iconify-icon>
            <span class="text-xs text-ink-muted">Formatted circuits &amp; sets</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="relative rounded-xl border border-warm-border bg-card p-8 shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="mb-6 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-amber-50 text-amber-600">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:smartphone-linear" stroke-width="1.5" class="text-2xl"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium tracking-tight text-ink">3. Client-ready instantly</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          No drag-and-drop busywork required. Your raw notes instantly become a polished, branded experience in your client's mobile app.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-md border border-warm-border bg-card p-3 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-parchment-alt flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium text-ink-muted">M</div>
            <div class="flex flex-col">
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-ink">Mike Davis</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-ink-muted">Program Updated</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:bell-linear" class="text-ink-muted"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
